WEBVTT

01:05.023 --> 01:06.941
It's prickly and irritated, right?

01:10.945 --> 01:13.865
Your bag looks heavy.
Why don't you take it off for now?

01:17.452 --> 01:20.163
This won't take long.
This one's an easy fix.

01:20.246 --> 01:21.998
It's fine. It's just a scratch.

01:22.082 --> 01:23.249
No, it isn't.

01:23.333 --> 01:25.960
I didn't want to bother you, ma'am.
I thought Si-won was here.

01:26.044 --> 01:27.754
I can see…

01:30.048 --> 01:31.633
…there's a curse in your eye.

01:31.716 --> 01:33.593
-What?
-A charm.

01:33.676 --> 01:36.888
A splinter with an evil charm
is lodged in your eyeball.

01:44.020 --> 01:45.730
Hold this tight to your eye.

01:46.356 --> 01:47.732
-Okay.
-Open your mouth.

01:47.816 --> 01:49.025
Only don't swallow it.

01:50.068 --> 01:51.569
-Hold it in there.
-Mm.

01:52.862 --> 01:55.198
Swish it around, then spit it in here.

01:55.698 --> 01:56.783
Spit it.

01:57.951 --> 01:59.077
The bag.

01:59.160 --> 01:59.994
Oh.

02:24.144 --> 02:25.895
It feels better now, right?

02:30.191 --> 02:32.861
What? Who needs a doctor?

02:32.944 --> 02:34.904
You can't compare
what I just did to a doctor.

02:34.988 --> 02:37.073
This has nothing to do with those idiots.

02:37.157 --> 02:38.449
Doctors are idiots?

02:38.533 --> 02:41.411
Anyone who can read a book
can become a doctor, Hye-ryung.

02:41.494 --> 02:43.496
You just have to put in the hours.

02:43.580 --> 02:45.999
What you do, and what I do,
is a unique talent.

02:46.833 --> 02:48.042
An innate gift.

02:48.126 --> 02:50.086
You're just born with it.

02:53.798 --> 02:56.676
You should go.
Don't wanna keep the runaway waiting.

02:58.511 --> 02:59.929
SI-WON

03:06.477 --> 03:07.854
Thank you so much.

03:08.646 --> 03:11.232
Remind her she needs to eat, okay?

03:46.267 --> 03:47.477
Oh my God.

03:48.019 --> 03:49.479
You really fell back asleep?

03:50.521 --> 03:51.773
Aren't you cold?

03:52.315 --> 03:55.693
You should sleep at your mom's
when it's cold. It's snowing outside.

03:55.777 --> 03:59.739
I'd rather freeze then smell like incense.
Isn't it kinda late for snow?

04:08.539 --> 04:12.377
Si-won, do you think
I could join the coding club with you?

04:14.879 --> 04:15.880
Hm.

04:27.976 --> 04:30.436
Hye-ryung! Slow down!

04:30.520 --> 04:33.231
-Hold up!
-I'm not waiting. I'll miss the bus again.

04:33.314 --> 04:34.774
We'll catch the next one.

04:34.857 --> 04:38.486
Come on, I didn't have breakfast.
Ah, shit. I hate you!

04:46.244 --> 04:48.079
Whoa! What the hell?

04:50.957 --> 04:53.126
-What was that?
-We can be late.

04:53.209 --> 04:54.669
-You should eat something.
-I'm good.

04:55.420 --> 04:57.088
It's right there. We can make it.

04:58.881 --> 05:00.008
Han Gi-tae?

05:00.508 --> 05:01.592
Huh?

05:02.677 --> 05:04.095
Oh!

05:04.971 --> 05:06.180
Are you crushing on Gi-tae?

05:07.265 --> 05:08.099
No.

05:08.975 --> 05:10.893
-Does he know?
-No, he doesn't.

05:10.977 --> 05:11.894
Don't tell anyone.

05:11.978 --> 05:13.521
Mm.

05:14.105 --> 05:15.690
What's he like?

05:15.773 --> 05:17.942
He's okay. He can't code for shit, though.

05:19.110 --> 05:20.069
Oh yeah.

05:21.529 --> 05:22.905
You got it bad, girl.

05:23.614 --> 05:25.366
I'll keep your secret. Don't worry.

05:26.701 --> 05:27.869
You really mean it?

05:29.037 --> 05:31.748
-You're keeping mine, aren't you?
-Hm.

05:32.248 --> 05:34.834
-Can you make room, please?
-Get in here. The kids'll scoot.

05:34.917 --> 05:37.170
-I like this spot.
-This one's got the heating.

05:37.253 --> 05:39.630
You take this spot.
The next bus could take a while.

05:39.714 --> 05:40.840
A bit more.

05:41.341 --> 05:43.384
All right. I think we're good now.

05:43.885 --> 05:45.678
-Thank you, girls.
-Mm-hmm.

05:46.179 --> 05:48.765
-I have to miss mahjong tonight.
-That's too bad.

05:51.601 --> 05:54.979
Hey. Why do you smell
like the incense my mother uses at home?

05:55.480 --> 05:57.982
-Did you stop by her house earlier?
-Yeah.

05:58.066 --> 05:59.359
I was worried.

06:02.904 --> 06:07.575
You sorta ghosted me and ignored my texts,
so I hoped the cold made you go there.

06:08.242 --> 06:10.828
I didn't go to see her,
but she did fix my eye infection.

06:10.912 --> 06:12.789
She only makes you think she can do stuff.

06:12.872 --> 06:15.083
You gotta stay away from that quack.
I already told you.

06:15.166 --> 06:16.125
Right.

06:18.002 --> 06:20.338
It does totally feel better
than before though.

06:20.421 --> 06:22.965
It stopped being red and prickly
after I saw your mom.

06:24.509 --> 06:26.427
You're supremely annoying. You know that?

06:26.511 --> 06:28.971
You're supremely annoying
when you ghost your best friend.

06:29.055 --> 06:30.598
Hey. I never go there.

06:30.681 --> 06:33.893
I don't need an escort to school.
And if I ever drop you, you'll know.

06:38.398 --> 06:42.068
Okay, I'll stop. I won't go to your mom's
anymore, or believe any of her stories.

06:42.151 --> 06:43.945
Hmm? I won't.

06:44.028 --> 06:47.907
I wouldn't mind so much if she was a real
shaman, not the crazy-ass village boozer.

06:48.533 --> 06:50.535
I shouldn't have gone. I'm sorry.

06:50.618 --> 06:51.744
Okay?

06:52.328 --> 06:55.498
OUR FACULTY AND STAFF SUPPORT
THE NEW BEGINNINGS OF ALL NEW STUDENTS

06:55.581 --> 06:56.833
SEORIN MIDDLE &amp; HIGH SCHOOL

07:00.628 --> 07:02.130
Hey, Si-won!

07:03.339 --> 07:06.926
I can't wait! I'm dying to know what kind
of app you came up with for the contest.

07:07.009 --> 07:08.302
It needs to be original.

07:08.803 --> 07:10.721
-I'll tell you guys about it later.
-Nice.

07:14.392 --> 07:17.812
Why haven't you joined the coding crew?
This genius must've taught you something.

07:17.895 --> 07:19.939
We were just talking about that.

07:20.022 --> 07:21.274
But she's not so techy.

07:22.358 --> 07:23.234
Really?

07:23.818 --> 07:25.027
What? Are you into art?

07:26.821 --> 07:28.990
She's into shamanism.

07:30.366 --> 07:31.367
Shamanism?

07:31.993 --> 07:33.578
Can you tell me my fortune?

07:34.454 --> 07:35.997
Or give me a tarot reading?

07:36.080 --> 07:38.291
Hey! Hee-jin.

07:44.380 --> 07:47.508
What's wrong?
You're actually here on time!

07:48.176 --> 07:51.471
The principal threatened me with
a month's detention if I show up late.

07:51.554 --> 07:54.682
I didn't even have breakfast yet.
We're going to the snack bar. You coming?

07:54.765 --> 07:56.767
Si-won! We're getting snacks.

08:01.397 --> 08:02.398
See you in class.

08:05.151 --> 08:06.235
We better hurry.

08:12.658 --> 08:15.828
You need to create phrases
to help you remember the formulas.

08:15.912 --> 08:17.580
Like E equals MC squared.

08:17.663 --> 08:19.749
Egor makes cookies two at a time.

08:19.832 --> 08:22.043
Stuff like that. Whatever works for you.

08:30.843 --> 08:33.304
Hey. I have to stay for coding.

08:33.387 --> 08:35.181
-I can wait.
-Si-won.

08:36.432 --> 08:37.433
Ready?

08:38.267 --> 08:39.393
I'll see you tomorrow.

08:48.778 --> 08:52.114
Isn't there a saying
that you should never drink alone? Huh?

08:52.198 --> 08:54.200
I'm never drinking alone.

08:54.283 --> 08:57.620
You know I'll have to report you
if you say it's for your daughter.

08:58.955 --> 09:00.957
I know you know what I was saying.

09:01.040 --> 09:03.543
If you're not convinced,
come on up to the green gate.

09:03.626 --> 09:06.629
If I wanna listen to a quack,
I'll get a duck.

09:06.712 --> 09:08.130
That's funny.

09:12.510 --> 09:14.095
But your prices aren't.

09:15.930 --> 09:16.847
Hm.

09:33.614 --> 09:36.158
You think you can hide from me like that?

09:42.123 --> 09:45.001
-Nice to see you again. Good night.
-You too.

09:45.084 --> 09:46.502
-Good night.
-Where's Si-won?

09:47.211 --> 09:49.755
-She had to go to coding club.
-That's a thing?

09:49.839 --> 09:52.216
-Mm-hmm.
-Have you eaten yet?

09:52.300 --> 09:53.342
I'll feed you.

09:55.052 --> 09:55.928
I can't.

09:56.554 --> 09:57.555
Why not?

09:59.599 --> 10:03.394
I know my house's energy speaks to you.
You're curious to see what's there.

10:05.146 --> 10:06.606
Have a good night.

10:22.580 --> 10:25.082
Damn, I missed the step again.

10:26.083 --> 10:27.084
Ouch.

10:27.585 --> 10:29.670
Oh. Oh, crap. Ow!

10:32.548 --> 10:35.718
Minister's Award, one team.
Governor's Award, one team.

10:35.801 --> 10:38.471
Superintendent of Education's Award,
two teams.

10:38.554 --> 10:41.057
Shit. Any one of these
would boost our applications.

10:42.642 --> 10:43.976
You gonna get us an award?

10:44.060 --> 10:46.187
If you come up with a good idea, sure.

10:46.270 --> 10:47.772
-Oh!
-What she said.

10:47.855 --> 10:51.275
I volunteer for snack duty.
Girl's gonna be pulling all-nighters.

10:51.359 --> 10:52.610
I'll pitch in on the UI.

10:52.693 --> 10:54.028
Then, I'm gonna

10:55.279 --> 10:56.572
grant you a wish of your choice.

10:56.656 --> 10:58.866
What the hell
would she be wanting from you?

10:58.949 --> 11:00.326
But Hye-ryung'd take you up on it.

11:00.409 --> 11:02.870
Don't you notice
her stealing glances on the sly?

11:02.953 --> 11:05.164
-Nope, but girl's got good taste.
-Dude.

11:06.207 --> 11:07.166
Girl's scary.

11:07.667 --> 11:08.793
She'll bewitch you.

11:08.876 --> 11:11.379
-No.
-Her mom's a shaman.

11:11.962 --> 11:15.383
And not just any shaman.
A whack job shaman murderer.

11:15.466 --> 11:17.468
Always with your crazy legends.

11:17.551 --> 11:18.928
I know this one's true!

11:19.011 --> 11:22.139
Listen. My cousin
went to Baekun Middle School,

11:22.223 --> 11:25.685
and he told me once that one
of the student's moms killed her husband.

11:26.644 --> 11:29.063
And that student was Do Hye-ryung.

11:30.815 --> 11:32.024
Is that true?

11:33.984 --> 11:35.778
-I totally see it.
-Seriously?

11:35.861 --> 11:38.489
I asked if she could read my fortune
when you mentioned shamanism.

11:39.615 --> 11:41.534
Can we just focus on the project?

11:41.617 --> 11:42.702
Shamanism.

11:43.536 --> 11:44.912
It's got a nice ring to it.

11:46.497 --> 11:48.833
It's an app contest, not a joke.

11:48.916 --> 11:51.752
But Gi-tae's joke is a really good idea.

11:51.836 --> 11:52.753
What?

11:52.837 --> 11:55.840
What you said before,
about granting her favors.

11:55.923 --> 11:59.385
And Hee-jin mentioned fortune-telling,
which is linked to saju.

12:00.010 --> 12:04.473
What if we threw it all together and made
it so our app magically grants wishes?

12:04.557 --> 12:06.559
Hey! Why are you so frigging hyper?

12:06.642 --> 12:10.062
Hey, yourself! I'm thinking
this could work. A "wishamism!"

12:10.646 --> 12:13.190
-Gonna drink soju?
-Saju. The four pillars.

12:13.274 --> 12:15.401
Using your birth date
to tell your fortune.

12:16.569 --> 12:17.987
Should Hye-ryung give us a lesson?

12:20.406 --> 12:24.160
If you guys keep acting like morons,
I'm gonna drop you.

12:28.456 --> 12:29.623
Si-won, wait!

12:31.667 --> 12:33.836
Fuck me. That bitch is scary.

12:49.685 --> 12:51.145
I told you.

12:51.687 --> 12:54.482
You have a connection to the energy here,

12:54.565 --> 12:56.066
and you couldn't stay away.

12:57.568 --> 12:59.612
Should I just leave this here for you?

12:59.695 --> 13:01.197
It doesn't go there.

13:02.072 --> 13:04.033
It goes in the room up above.

13:08.162 --> 13:11.290
You've been dying to know
what's in there, haven't you?

13:11.373 --> 13:14.335
It's been calling to you
since you came for your eye.

13:16.086 --> 13:17.129
You have permission.

13:36.232 --> 13:37.233
Hye-ryung.

13:38.108 --> 13:41.487
Come on! The point
wasn't for you to just stand there.

14:07.012 --> 14:09.098
It's strangely soothing, isn't it?

14:47.219 --> 14:48.554
They're so cute.

14:49.263 --> 14:50.764
Choose anything in the room.

14:52.057 --> 14:53.893
It will be my present to you.

15:10.367 --> 15:11.744
Were you

15:11.827 --> 15:13.704
drawn to that doll?

15:16.665 --> 15:18.667
-What kind of doll is this?
-Deolmi.

15:19.627 --> 15:20.544
From

15:21.211 --> 15:22.755
a word that means "scruff."

15:22.838 --> 15:26.342
It lets you drag people around
however you want,

15:26.425 --> 15:27.760
if you ask it to.

15:29.428 --> 15:30.554
I can show you how.

15:30.638 --> 15:32.348
-Huh?
-I'll teach you.

15:33.098 --> 15:35.059
In case you ever need a good curse.

15:38.729 --> 15:39.730
Here.

15:41.482 --> 15:44.610
Uh, you need
something related to the person

15:45.486 --> 15:47.154
you'd like to grab by the scruff.

15:48.113 --> 15:51.158
I like to use things
like fingernails, toenails, or hair.

15:51.241 --> 15:53.827
You tie it to the doll with a silk thread.

15:54.328 --> 15:58.666
And finally, you carve
the eyes, nose, and mouth on the face.

15:58.749 --> 16:02.044
You write their saju here,
and make sure to spray all over…

16:02.127 --> 16:04.588
Ha! …so that the silk thread turns red.

16:04.672 --> 16:06.507
-Spray?
-Blood.

16:07.091 --> 16:08.926
That can't be right.

16:09.009 --> 16:10.511
Why can't it?

16:11.011 --> 16:14.348
That's what allows you to put the curse.
Fresh, hot blood.

16:32.533 --> 16:34.368
I told you this before.

16:34.451 --> 16:35.911
You're special.

16:36.537 --> 16:38.539
If you do what I showed you

16:38.622 --> 16:40.457
and prepare the deolmi,

16:40.541 --> 16:43.043
you can shake whoever you want
as you please.

16:43.127 --> 16:44.837
Why would I want to do that?

16:44.920 --> 16:47.006
Do you want to be my daughter?

16:47.089 --> 16:49.174
My spirit daughter?

16:52.636 --> 16:55.097
If you're home,
you should greet me properly.

16:55.180 --> 16:58.183
Stop sneaking around my house
like a thief.

16:58.267 --> 17:01.437
I'd rather be a thief than a drunk
who drove my dad to suicide.

17:04.982 --> 17:06.108
Si-won!

17:06.817 --> 17:08.527
I can explain. I only came here because--

17:08.610 --> 17:11.155
You lying bitch!
Save it for someone who cares.

17:11.655 --> 17:14.033
You pretended to be my friend.
All you wanted was ammunition.

17:14.116 --> 17:16.660
I wasn't pretending, Si-won.

17:16.744 --> 17:18.203
You're fucking dead to me.

17:51.570 --> 17:54.948
I would never… hurt you.

18:18.806 --> 18:19.932
I can explain.

18:29.983 --> 18:32.903
Have you ever heard that
if you write your saju and make a wish,

18:32.986 --> 18:34.363
it'll come true?

18:40.369 --> 18:42.454
The smell of incense
makes me want to puke.

18:42.538 --> 18:45.249
I wanna scream
when I remember the looks I got

18:45.332 --> 18:47.376
from the lowlifes
who knew I was the shaman's kid.

18:47.459 --> 18:49.711
The crazy lady
who drove my dad to his death.

18:49.795 --> 18:54.550
And I wanna disappear when I hear
my drunken mom spout her spirit nonsense.

18:54.633 --> 18:57.427
FEBRUARY 1, 2005
KWON SI-WON

19:05.894 --> 19:07.437
I wish she'd die already.

19:11.525 --> 19:12.985
I think it's a good wish.

19:13.861 --> 19:15.737
You have something you wish for?

19:17.322 --> 19:18.240
What?

19:24.204 --> 19:26.415
I'm asking you what you would wish for.

19:27.916 --> 19:28.750
Oh.

19:35.549 --> 19:37.009
I wish for your forgiveness.

19:37.092 --> 19:38.260
Not that stuff.

19:41.096 --> 19:44.683
It has to be something you've wished for
for a really long time.

19:46.852 --> 19:48.979
That you've never told anyone.

19:50.731 --> 19:52.941
Your deepest, most heartfelt desire.

20:02.409 --> 20:03.368
I want…

20:05.495 --> 20:06.997
Gi-tae to like me.

20:19.509 --> 20:21.845
So, your secret desire
is to go out on a date?

20:26.892 --> 20:28.393
He is cute.

20:29.186 --> 20:30.062
Do it.

20:30.854 --> 20:31.772
Do what?

20:39.696 --> 20:41.031
I wish that, uh…

20:41.114 --> 20:42.282
MARCH 12, 2005
DO HYE-RYUNG

20:42.366 --> 20:43.992
…Gi-tae would ask me out.

20:46.954 --> 20:47.788
No.

20:48.372 --> 20:50.874
I wish that Gi-tae
would kind of fall for me.

20:50.958 --> 20:53.252
No! You sound
like you're ordering take out.

20:57.547 --> 20:59.633
It has to come from the heart
and sound sincere.

21:00.217 --> 21:02.719
Like how I confessed
what my biggest wish is before.

21:03.595 --> 21:05.013
And sound like you mean it.

21:05.097 --> 21:08.267
None of this "Uh… uh… kinda" crap.

21:08.767 --> 21:10.394
-You need passion.
-I… I can't.

21:10.477 --> 21:11.645
"I can't" is not allowed.

21:11.728 --> 21:14.481
Can't somebody else help you?
I'm not even in coding club.

21:14.564 --> 21:17.317
The line is, "fall in love with me,"
not just "for me."

21:17.818 --> 21:18.735
Watch me.

21:20.570 --> 21:24.658
I wish for Gi-tae to fall in love with me!

21:24.741 --> 21:26.201
That was loud!

21:26.285 --> 21:29.579
Mm. This is so frigging embarrassing.

21:30.372 --> 21:33.667
-You gotta put yourself out there.
-Like you know all about that?

21:38.463 --> 21:39.589
I wish for

21:40.090 --> 21:41.842
Han Gi-tae to fall for me.

21:41.925 --> 21:45.095
Please, make him fall in love with me!

21:45.971 --> 21:50.726
My name is Do Hye-ryung, and I want
Gi-tae to fall madly in love with me!

22:01.528 --> 22:02.654
Sometimes,

22:03.155 --> 22:04.948
you scare the shit out of me.

22:10.871 --> 22:11.705
Why?

22:12.205 --> 22:14.708
You know all my deepest secrets.

22:16.752 --> 22:19.212
I'll keep all your secrets safe, Si-won.

22:24.760 --> 22:27.095
You know the main reason
people hate my mother?

22:27.179 --> 22:29.639
'Cause it's impossible
to hide things from her.

22:31.767 --> 22:33.310
That's her biggest gift.

22:34.936 --> 22:37.105
Everyone has something
they wanna keep hidden.

22:37.689 --> 22:39.024
For me, it's my mother.

22:48.575 --> 22:49.826
You know I mean it.

22:50.702 --> 22:51.953
I won't tell anyone.

22:52.662 --> 22:54.081
If you think it's better,

22:55.374 --> 22:57.250
I'll stay away from you at school.

23:04.591 --> 23:05.717
Forget that.

23:10.097 --> 23:12.808
I can just blackmail you with this video.

23:12.891 --> 23:14.434
-Give me that!
-It's so good!

23:14.518 --> 23:16.770
-Give that, you weasel!
-Too late. It's done!

23:16.853 --> 23:18.939
Delete that stupid thing.

23:19.022 --> 23:21.900
-Please, delete it.
-No way. Now sleep! It's late. Sleep.

23:21.983 --> 23:22.818
Sweet dreams.

23:22.901 --> 23:24.486
-Delete it.
-Night.

23:24.569 --> 23:26.988
I'm not going to sleep
until you delete that video!

23:29.950 --> 23:32.619
Your wish app is really cool.
I think you'll win.

23:33.120 --> 23:34.371
-You do?
-Mm.

23:34.454 --> 23:36.164
It's simple but exciting.

23:36.248 --> 23:40.001
I've been having butterflies in my stomach
ever since I made the wish video with you.

23:41.086 --> 23:42.546
Even if it doesn't come true,

23:43.046 --> 23:45.715
I'm really glad we did it together,
and shared our secrets.

23:47.008 --> 23:50.011
-It stays between the two of us though.
-Mm-hmm. Of course.

23:55.475 --> 23:59.604
And, but, or, nor, for, so, yet.
These are the coordinate conjunctions.

23:59.688 --> 24:00.647
GIRIGO
MAKE A WISH

24:00.730 --> 24:04.526
When you have two independent clauses,
each clause has a subject and a verb

24:04.609 --> 24:06.695
linked by a coordinate conjunction.

24:06.778 --> 24:08.321
You put a comma before it.

24:08.405 --> 24:09.865
For example, the teacher…

24:09.948 --> 24:12.909
DO HYE-RYUNG
HOW'S THIS FOR THE GIRIGO ICON?

24:12.993 --> 24:16.621
"The teacher graded" has a subject
and a verb. "Everyone got" does also.

24:16.705 --> 24:17.789
Kwon Si-won?

24:18.665 --> 24:20.459
No phones in class.

24:21.835 --> 24:22.794
Sorry, ma'am.

24:23.753 --> 24:26.673
If you have a dependent clause
followed by an independent clause,

24:26.756 --> 24:27.716
you also use a comma.

24:28.675 --> 24:30.260
For example, "Since it was cold out."

24:41.646 --> 24:43.023
I'll have to double-check.

24:50.530 --> 24:52.782
I think I manifested something
with the video.

24:52.866 --> 24:55.410
Gi-tae made eye contact
twice with me today.

24:55.494 --> 24:58.497
-Of course. You did what I said.
-Mm.

24:59.080 --> 25:01.833
You put your whole heart into it.

25:02.792 --> 25:04.544
You really like him that much?

25:04.628 --> 25:06.171
-I don't know.
-Oh.

25:08.882 --> 25:10.383
I'm cutting you off!

25:11.843 --> 25:14.054
-I need them. I can pay.
-Crazy bitch.

25:14.137 --> 25:16.223
Don't come back!

25:16.306 --> 25:18.099
-I gotta go.
-Why are you doing this?

25:18.183 --> 25:20.185
I told you why. Quit making a scene.

25:20.268 --> 25:22.771
-Get out and stay out!
-I have money! I can pay!

25:25.857 --> 25:27.150
Stop calling me a drunk!

25:27.234 --> 25:29.986
SI-WON, DON'T STRESS TOO MUCH…
YOUR MOM…

25:39.579 --> 25:43.833
I'M AT THE HIDEOUT. WHEN ARE YOU COMING?

26:00.308 --> 26:02.477
Hey, runaway. Have you eaten?

26:02.978 --> 26:04.354
So rude.

26:05.063 --> 26:08.149
Show some respect.
I brought you into this world.

26:10.193 --> 26:11.236
Si-won!

26:12.862 --> 26:13.863
Bye.

26:13.947 --> 26:14.948
Shit.

26:24.291 --> 26:27.127
I MIGHT JUST SLEEP AT HOME TONIGHT!
SEE YOU TOMORROW!

26:36.636 --> 26:40.932
I MIGHT JUST SLEEP AT HOME TONIGHT!
SEE YOU TOMORROW!

27:06.499 --> 27:07.959
What did she do?

27:18.511 --> 27:20.513
So much blood.

28:39.801 --> 28:41.177
Hair.

28:41.261 --> 28:42.429
Si-won's hair.

28:46.433 --> 28:47.559
SEORIN

28:56.192 --> 28:57.402
My daughter, Si-won.

28:58.361 --> 28:59.529
Please, my daughter.

29:01.781 --> 29:03.491
Heavenly spirit, forgive my daughter.

29:05.452 --> 29:06.828
She didn't know what she was doing.

29:06.911 --> 29:09.330
I pray to the Bulsa Jeseok for mercy.

29:09.414 --> 29:11.916
If someone must pay for her mistake,
please punish me.

29:12.000 --> 29:15.295
Please, punish me instead of my daughter.
Si-won didn't mean it.

29:15.378 --> 29:17.964
I beg your mercy, your forgiveness.
Spare my child.

29:18.047 --> 29:19.549
GIRIGO
MAKE A WISH

30:10.350 --> 30:12.685
The person
you are trying to reach is unav--

30:55.728 --> 30:56.729
Hye-ryung!

31:04.988 --> 31:06.281
Don't go!

31:07.740 --> 31:08.825
I need you…

31:08.908 --> 31:10.660
…to protect my daughter with this.

31:12.078 --> 31:13.621
Put this amulet…

31:14.122 --> 31:16.124
Put it inside her school bag.

31:16.207 --> 31:17.959
But she can't know it's in there.

31:18.042 --> 31:22.964
That girl takes after her father. She'll
want nothing to do with this protection.

31:23.047 --> 31:25.592
She's in grave danger.

31:25.675 --> 31:28.052
If you don't do this, she'll die.

31:28.136 --> 31:30.513
I couldn't save my h… husband,

31:30.597 --> 31:33.182
but I… I can't lose her
to what she's unleashed.

31:33.892 --> 31:35.101
You hear me?

31:35.184 --> 31:36.811
Why don't you say something?!

31:36.895 --> 31:37.854
Huh?

31:41.274 --> 31:43.067
You need to go to a doctor.

31:46.905 --> 31:50.575
You remember
how I fixed your cursed splinter?

31:50.658 --> 31:53.328
I'll heal myself now that that's done.

31:53.828 --> 31:55.246
You go save Si-won.

31:58.625 --> 31:59.792
Get out of here!

32:03.504 --> 32:04.714
Go to school!

32:05.214 --> 32:09.177
And hide the amulet.
My daughter will die without it!

32:41.501 --> 32:42.502
Si-won.

32:43.628 --> 32:45.463
-I went to your house before.
-What?

32:53.596 --> 32:54.555
And then what?

32:55.223 --> 32:56.099
Uh…

32:57.934 --> 32:58.768
Your…

33:03.398 --> 33:04.524
I'm sorry.

33:10.780 --> 33:12.490
-What's with her?
-Mm-mm.

33:13.658 --> 33:16.035
The Road Away by Kim So-wol.

33:16.536 --> 33:18.162
Yesterday, again, at an inn

33:18.246 --> 33:20.873
I spent a sleepless night
With the cawing crows

33:20.957 --> 33:24.377
Today, how many more "ri" on my journey
I don't know whither?

33:24.877 --> 33:28.172
That girl… …takes after her father.

33:29.465 --> 33:32.051
She'll want nothing
to do with this protection.

33:33.261 --> 33:34.595
She's in grave danger.

33:34.679 --> 33:37.098
If you don't do this, she'll die.

33:37.181 --> 33:39.726
I couldn't save my husband,

33:39.809 --> 33:42.186
but I… I can't lose her
to what she's unleashed.

33:44.188 --> 33:45.732
Look at the geese in midair

33:45.815 --> 33:48.568
Are they flying so well
Because there's a path?

33:48.651 --> 33:52.488
Look at the geese in midair
I'm standing right at a crossroads

34:02.457 --> 34:04.834
-Can't this wait?
-If I don't do it now, I'll forget.

34:04.917 --> 34:05.752
Whatever.

34:09.964 --> 34:10.798
Yo!

34:13.301 --> 34:14.552
What are you doing?

34:31.944 --> 34:33.571
Y… your mom wants me to--

35:18.282 --> 35:21.494
It was freaking brutal.
Just smack, across her face.

35:21.994 --> 35:24.789
-She ripped the paper to shreds.
-Why would she need an amulet?

35:24.872 --> 35:26.958
Yeah, she could kill someone
with one look.

35:27.041 --> 35:30.711
Have you noticed she changes the subject
whenever we talk about shamanism?

35:31.212 --> 35:34.132
Is it because
she's actually related to the quack?

35:34.757 --> 35:36.134
Maybe.

35:36.217 --> 35:39.053
After she got caught,
Hye-ryung said something.

35:39.887 --> 35:41.722
It might not mean anything.

35:42.431 --> 35:44.976
-It was so tense. I was freaking out.
-Ah.

35:45.059 --> 35:46.102
What did she say?

35:46.185 --> 35:48.312
Stop being so dramatic and just tell us!

35:48.396 --> 35:51.816
This morning,
Hye-ryung was acting weird with Si-won.

35:51.899 --> 35:53.234
Kind of cagey, you know?

35:53.317 --> 35:54.610
She's gonna pay for this.

35:54.694 --> 35:56.821
The amulet, she said,
"It's your mom who wants--"

35:58.823 --> 35:59.824
You came?

36:06.873 --> 36:08.166
Come check this out.

36:08.708 --> 36:09.959
The app's good to go.

36:10.042 --> 36:12.128
-We're done?
-It's ready?

36:13.337 --> 36:14.881
How'd you get it done so fast?

36:14.964 --> 36:16.549
Don't you think it looks

36:16.632 --> 36:17.967
too serious?

36:19.051 --> 36:19.927
I love it.

36:20.011 --> 36:22.805
Like your opinion counts, asshole.

36:24.891 --> 36:26.726
You can all shut your mouths.

36:27.351 --> 36:28.186
I coded it.

36:28.853 --> 36:29.854
I made it.

36:30.855 --> 36:32.106
While you were

36:32.690 --> 36:33.941
busy spreading rumors.

36:34.025 --> 36:36.527
But you did help with the design.

36:36.611 --> 36:40.531
I heard what you said before I came in.
And how I'm related to that shaman.

36:41.657 --> 36:43.117
But shamanism was your idea.

36:46.245 --> 36:49.957
Gi-tae, you didn't do much,
but you did promise

36:50.917 --> 36:52.627
you'd grant me a wish.

37:29.247 --> 37:30.081
Hey,

37:30.998 --> 37:32.083
ever heard of Girigo?

37:32.583 --> 37:33.417
What?

37:36.420 --> 37:39.131
Girigo's a cool new app
that grants wishes.

37:39.215 --> 37:40.216
Giri what?

37:41.759 --> 37:42.969
I wish for

37:43.469 --> 37:44.845
Han Gi-tae to fall for me!

37:44.929 --> 37:45.972
What is this?

37:47.431 --> 37:49.725
Please make him fall in love with me!

37:52.645 --> 37:53.729
Oh my God!

37:53.813 --> 37:57.942
My name is Do Hye-ryung, and I want Gi-tae
to fall madly in love with me!

37:58.025 --> 37:59.568
Let's get the screen in there!

37:59.652 --> 38:03.281
Might as well jump off a bridge now!

38:04.782 --> 38:07.743
-What a dweeb!
-You know this is for real.

38:09.787 --> 38:11.872
My phone's blowing up.

38:12.373 --> 38:14.792
Now the whole school knows she likes him.

38:14.875 --> 38:17.420
Maybe just ask the guy out for coffee?

38:17.503 --> 38:21.716
My name is Do Hye-ryung, and I want Gi-tae
to fall madly in love with me!

38:22.383 --> 38:25.177
Please make him fall in love with me.

38:25.261 --> 38:26.429
Gi-tae, you're so hot!

38:26.512 --> 38:29.432
I want Gi-tae
to fall madly in love with me!

38:29.515 --> 38:31.559
Please fall in love with my sorry ass!

38:31.642 --> 38:33.352
Hey.

38:34.228 --> 38:36.397
Shamanism?

38:37.648 --> 38:38.649
I don't know what's worse.

38:38.733 --> 38:41.861
That she's your mother,
or that you're into that crazy shit too.

38:41.944 --> 38:42.862
The quack?

38:46.240 --> 38:48.451
She looks like she's gonna cry.

38:48.534 --> 38:51.412
What's the matter, huh?
Someone put a curse on you, huh?

38:51.495 --> 38:53.831
So you can't say
any more stupid shit? Huh?

38:54.623 --> 38:56.959
-You can't film this.
-It's too good not to.

38:57.793 --> 39:01.839
Hey! Why would I ever
want to go out with a loser like you?

39:03.007 --> 39:04.091
-Oh!
-Oh!

39:04.175 --> 39:07.345
You embarrassed me.
And you need to fucking apologize.

39:16.437 --> 39:17.355
Whoa, bitch.

39:18.230 --> 39:19.440
You're dead!

39:26.906 --> 39:28.240
HAN GI-TAE

39:30.951 --> 39:31.911
Satisfied?

39:56.685 --> 39:57.603
HAN GI-TAE

40:00.272 --> 40:03.526
You need something related to the person
you'd like to grab by the scruff.

40:04.527 --> 40:07.279
I like to use things
like fingernails, toenails or hair.

40:08.531 --> 40:11.283
You tie it to the doll with a silk thread.

40:12.034 --> 40:14.870
And finally, you carve
the eyes, nose, and mouth on the face.

40:15.621 --> 40:17.248
You write their saju here…

40:18.249 --> 40:21.335
…and make sure to spray all over
so that the silk thread turns red.

40:21.419 --> 40:22.461
Ha!

40:25.214 --> 40:27.216
-Spray?
-Blood.

40:27.299 --> 40:30.886
Fresh, hot blood.
That's what allows you to put the curse.

40:33.556 --> 40:35.808
MARCH 12, 2005
DO HYE-RYUNG

40:45.860 --> 40:49.196
It's important to have
a connection to this energy.

40:49.697 --> 40:51.782
It's not something just anyone can do.

40:52.408 --> 40:54.201
It requires a gift?

40:54.285 --> 40:58.664
Yes. But in this case,
what really matters is the intention

40:59.206 --> 41:00.624
in your heart.

41:02.293 --> 41:04.503
And the heart must be guided by the mind,

41:04.587 --> 41:06.797
which is both the root and master.

41:07.298 --> 41:11.552
And the master will require payment
equivalent to the control desired.

41:13.012 --> 41:16.515
An arm is at least
the blood of one chicken.

41:17.016 --> 41:19.393
And it goes up if you want more control.

41:20.811 --> 41:22.938
If you want to control both arms,

41:23.022 --> 41:25.566
you need to offer something bigger,
like a pig.

41:26.650 --> 41:28.235
The rules are simple.

41:31.155 --> 41:33.407
You write down your saju and make a wish…

41:35.701 --> 41:36.869
and it comes true.

41:37.870 --> 41:39.914
You have no idea.

41:41.123 --> 41:43.667
I'll make the wish
just the way you wanted.

41:45.002 --> 41:46.420
My wish is…

41:55.262 --> 41:56.514
…for all of you to die.

42:07.942 --> 42:09.360
That's my true wish.

42:23.207 --> 42:24.375
Si-won!

42:24.458 --> 42:25.543
Did you see it?

42:26.043 --> 42:27.920
You need to wipe that shit out.

42:28.003 --> 42:30.506
This is your fault.
Delete it before it goes viral!

42:31.715 --> 42:34.885
Of course I saw it.
I'm on it, asshole! I'm already at school!

42:46.772 --> 42:47.731
DELETE FOLDER

43:20.472 --> 43:21.724
MULTIMEDIA ROOM CLOUD SERVER

43:47.791 --> 43:48.792
Oh my God.

43:56.425 --> 43:58.636
You're wondering what the bitch is up to?

44:01.180 --> 44:02.681
The rules are simple.

44:03.307 --> 44:05.601
I'll make the wish
just the way you wanted.

44:08.062 --> 44:09.480
My wish is…

44:13.984 --> 44:15.402
for all of you to die.

44:15.486 --> 44:16.612
Crazy bitch!

44:18.530 --> 44:19.573
It was our secret.

44:19.657 --> 44:22.743
I truly want every single one of you dead.

44:40.010 --> 44:42.096
That's my true wish.

44:57.820 --> 44:59.488
How could you do this?

45:15.170 --> 45:18.132
You'll be sorry, Do Hye-ryung!

46:04.762 --> 46:05.888
SENDING WISH…

46:06.513 --> 46:08.891
YOUR WISH HAS BEEN GRANTED

46:20.194 --> 46:27.201
YOUR WISH HAS BEEN GRANTED

46:27.284 --> 46:31.663
IF WISHES COULD KILL
